    "path": "src/agent/task",
    "name": "task",
    "purpose": "Owns agent task runtime state. Task keeps public construction, preview, worker routing, and direct session_tx event sending in task.rs; TaskState stores the original user request, step_count, steps, and a PlanQueue-backed plan_queue. task_step.rs creates the initial Plan from user_request, inserts plans into PlanQueue with generated StepSignatures, runs plans from queued signatures, records completed steps through PlanQueue::complete_step, and only parses/starts a follow-up Plan after every stored step in the completed plan has finished.",
